channel.description:
Welcome to the official YouTube channel of Jewish News One (JN1), the world's first Jewish news network. 
JN1 is an independently-owned 24hr TV news channel broadcasting in rolling video news format. The JN1 mission is to offer global audiences a uniquely Jewish perspective on the issues shaping today's world, while also providing viewers with fresh insight and added context. 
JN1 currently broadcasts via 3 international satellites and can also be viewed via a growing selection of individual domestic cable operators - please speak to your cable TV provider for details. The channel broadcasts in two languages (English and Russian).
